00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:27,320
A propitious omen is approaching?

294
00:31:29,479 --> 00:31:31,800
Why would Shanxi experience
a locust plague?

295
00:31:32,519 --> 00:31:34,160
Why would Henan experience floods?

296
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:37,600
Why are there bandits in Liang Mountain?

297
00:31:46,800 --> 00:31:48,959
