and the imperial saber was taken.

307
00:32:18,439 --> 00:32:19,400
Official He

308
00:32:19,719 --> 00:32:21,600
was obviously buttering up His Majesty.

309
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:29,600
Official Fu,

310
00:32:30,239 --> 00:32:31,360
please rise.

311
00:32:32,120 --> 00:32:34,880
His Majesty is waiting for you
at the Imperial Study.

312
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:40,679
Take it slow.

313
00:32:40,999 --> 00:32:41,759
Come.

314
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:04,400
You...

315
00:33:06,199 --> 00:33:08,800
When will you win credit for me?

316
00:33:15,719 --> 00:33:16,959
You've sat on your knees for so long.

317
00:33:19,759 --> 00:33:21,479
Do you know what you've done wrong?

318
00:33:22,279 --> 00:33:23,600
I was careless

319
00:33:24,360 --> 00:33:25,199
and incompetent.

320
00:33:25,439 --> 00:33:27,360
Causing Your Majesty's imperial saber
to be taken by the bad guys.

321
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:29,239
Please punish me.

322
00:33:31,999 --> 00:33:33,519
Careless?

323
00:33:35,239 --> 00:33:36,080
How are you going to settle it?

324
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,880
I'll go after the fugitives right away.

325
00:33:39,279 --> 00:33:40,120
To get the imperial saber back.

326
00:33:40,719 --> 00:33:42,600
And I'll punish the officials
who don't fulfill their duties.

327
00:33:45,560 --> 00:33:46,679
You still don't get it.

328
00:33:57,479 --> 00:33:58,400
What's next?

329
00:34:09,479 --> 00:34:11,920
The scholars violate the rules
with words;

330
00:34:13,199 --> 00:34:15,120
