(The mother of Fu Kang'an)

340
00:35:10,080 --> 00:35:11,719
The local official was incompetent.

341
00:35:11,959 --> 00:35:13,840
The tribute, a saber, was taken.

342
00:35:14,279 --> 00:35:16,120
Why would he be so angry?

343
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,679
The local official was killed.

344
00:35:20,199 --> 00:35:21,279
And the imperial saber was taken.

345
00:35:21,479 --> 00:35:22,479
You're a chief.

346
00:35:22,719 --> 00:35:23,959
But it took almost a year
for you to know that.

347
00:35:24,719 --> 00:35:25,999
How could His Majesty not be angry?

348
00:35:29,279 --> 00:35:30,600
Do you really think

349
00:35:31,279 --> 00:35:33,400
it was just about the imperial saber?

350
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:36,959
You mean...

351
00:35:38,759 --> 00:35:40,360
Since His Majesty ascended the throne,

352
00:35:40,519 --> 00:35:41,719
the country has been peaceful.

353
00:35:42,719 --> 00:35:43,800
All nations worship our country.

354
00:35:44,199 --> 00:35:45,280
In such prosperous time,

355
00:35:45,680 --> 00:35:47,320
