00:35:59,999 --> 00:36:02,760
Looks like you've
finally realised it.

360
00:36:05,519 --> 00:36:08,119
No one knows His Majesty
better than me.

361
00:36:08,880 --> 00:36:12,119
The Red Flower Club is
like a thorn to him.

